{"id": "1237182679426924644", "channel_id": "1237182679426924644", "type": 0, "author_id": "969319742718509056", "author_name": "15828894371", "author_bot": false, "content": "當年要不是24帶隊，我還在打325呢，當然，打325也沒什麼不好，但是350對我來說可以更加的海闊天空嘛。\n1-3上紅花，隊友帶兩個r命輪可以加40黑印，可以買兩個黃金造物或者多覺醒一個隊友。有“我們的家”造物時可以穩過。\n其他：24帶隊可以穩定過一關，水母打3-3。希洛莉莉打4-3剩下的打2-3。", "timestamp": "2024-05-06T23:22:16.518000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1237182679917662208", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-13-03-811_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 152211, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1237182679426924644/1237182679917662208/Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-13-03-811_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbae68&is=69ca5ce8&hm=db9883d1e7117448248f9dd7703379fde6f9875b0f2e2d24f933d9f09908ae1d&"}, {"id": "1237182680437882880", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-13-00-602_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 150404, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1237182679426924644/1237182680437882880/Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-13-00-602_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbae68&is=69ca5ce8&hm=97248237375bfbd48016c3914a5a0c94a234f6cdb4d9dea08f6d1896cbe6eb05&"}, {"id": "1237182680852987956", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-12-57-857_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 158537, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1237182679426924644/1237182680852987956/Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-12-57-857_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbae68&is=69ca5ce8&hm=85926e014740794bde2d387898d49027cc3d52b730920f632fee544d38f39d03&"}, {"id": "1237182681222217838", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-12-54-620_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 154430, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1237182679426924644/1237182681222217838/Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-12-54-620_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbae68&is=69ca5ce8&hm=3fbb5036b1633251cfa12e539e0c19f7d03d14a4fa090b9e8d720a1e56434c3e&"}, {"id": "1237182681641517177", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-12-46-599_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 156010, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1237182679426924644/1237182681641517177/Screenshot_2024-05-07-07-12-46-599_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69cbae69&is=69ca5ce9&hm=6255e0f6d69dc37457934c448b75730aecd401f3c9b2386c748e97ec1634f394&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1237182679426924644", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "分享一下自己的融災350配隊", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1236929999781494784", "channel_id": "1236929999781494784", "type": 0, "author_id": "597345991632486406", "author_name": "whimsical_starfish_19845", "author_bot": false, "content": "此篇寫給那些有一定練度、角色，不想凹融災的玩家的配隊參考攻略。\n\n  看圖可以發現，角色很多啟靈都是0，技能為3-5，但依舊能過，因此應該能適用於守密人等級60，遊玩遊戲2個月以上的玩家。\n\n  以下分別介紹各關的關鍵角色或刻印，造物刻印沒有也無所謂，我是一次打過的，遠遠沒有打到上限，所以請放心嘗試。(隊伍配置參考了版上天玄的攻略)\n\n(以下按照打的順序介紹)\n第五關：\n  看到潘就帶旺達，然後配這三隻其餘隊伍比較少用且適配旺達的角色，主要要求旺達高練，可以借助戰。打起來難度稍高。\n\n第四關：\n  血肉羅坦，希莉雙打會更優，神父隊也可。應該是本次最吃練度的關卡，除了複製事件要複製關鍵牌外，沒什麼技巧，純拚練度。\n  我不玩血肉，因此低練就上了。打起來難度感受最高，但由於剛好造物夠好，也是一次過，如果練度拉一些會輕鬆許多。(從這關可以看出，當前血肉的強度是非常高的，建議難關用血肉上)\n\n第三關：\n  關鍵:帶水母、拉蒙，都非常適配本關時靈擺。\n  深海沒地方丟，就丟這關了，0啟圖魯，1啟墨菲的練度，打起來毫無壓力，死抗都用不到。莉莉打的傷害不高，也都是單次，非常適合深海和死抗，可以帶個懲戒保險。莉莉覺醒後先打技能牌，讓他召喚小隻的黑球是最好的。\n水母洗牌，並補點傷害，有鏡像可以印水母2。\n\n第二關：\n  神父隊或燉雞，記得帶暴食加血，如果練度真的不足，可以凹一張鏡像給神父2或心眼，本隊有神父就不需要艾爾瓦，純粹是湊數用。\n  只要拿血量，疊盾，然後配上時靈擺用報償、應消之苦，或心眼敲下去，就能無腦過。\n  本關王皆為單下攻擊，死抗角色如菲茵特非常適合。\n\n第一關：\n  剛好剩下莉茲隊，就帶了，但不是那麼適合，只要帶能每回合打五張牌的隊伍就行了。難度普普。\n\n  以上是本次融災攻略，打起來難度相較之前低了不少，希望能幫助到有一定練度，但還沒350的人。\n\n如有任何的疑問都歡迎留言。", "timestamp": "2024-05-06T06:38:12.996000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-06T09:52:58.286000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1236930000050192405", "filename": "5.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 174775, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1236929999781494784/1236930000050192405/5.JPG?ex=69cc1495&is=69cac315&hm=3b306337130e336b81e4074d53fc6cbdce879ee8801feeb058e6ff758e43d738&"}, {"id": "1236930000318365706", "filename": "4.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 175067, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1236929999781494784/1236930000318365706/4.JPG?ex=69cc1495&is=69cac315&hm=6f55a45e2989c2b335f1511092927e697c562011667d0c5b79b151fe4af7196a&"}, {"id": "1236930000566091776", "filename": "3.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 184600, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1236929999781494784/1236930000566091776/3.JPG?ex=69cc1495&is=69cac315&hm=7b60f589dd0e092de8274944eb36bb15360364c2f2e760881035b5ca6ce4b3a0&"}, {"id": "1236930001018818580", "filename": "2.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 174319, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1236929999781494784/1236930001018818580/2.JPG?ex=69cc1495&is=69cac315&hm=493d18d43e784b2e206fe0368a33be070fcc714d5593d89213e6f884d6e78b36&"}, {"id": "1236930001316610088", "filename": "1.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 174861, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1236929999781494784/1236930001316610088/1.JPG?ex=69cc1495&is=69cac315&hm=3b1ffdc84ac9664e382f07be8953082869fdc1eb4eb8a354d7dc09ab5e3ccc2d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1236929999781494784", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "普通練度不用凹的350融災攻略", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
